br />\n離心力反面少"},{"pid":"558c89ddb439a99185959d81081b3cf6717e5fa1","tid":527282,"uid":122892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:59:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e9a6b2204955d92ce786d82037b5f042799dc29","tid":527282,"uid":69340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"係咁一開始就會升你個人上去?"},{"pid":"f2195c6963f0b57108f6dbcf9dcf38e7d9e846c7","tid":527282,"uid":69340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:08:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪一開始就會升你個人上去?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"50a0fdaa30a576ba05fc3998b1f7451bf2049155","tid":527282,"uid":81783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:14:05.000Z","msg":"如果你連USJ普通既過山車(倒後倒前)果個都頂唔住...千祈唔好玩飛龍....."},{"pid":"e78ff13447376c61cfbc0db057bf64e98a1be5cc","tid":527282,"uid":137006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:22:25.000Z","msg":"自己連玩香港Disney U型驚<br />\n但個人覺得飛龍除左第一下面向地衝外<br />\n其他冇乜驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係好敢玩機動遊戲俾frd局住上去玩"},{"pid":"4889ec1a5e18fa16264027358e7ad353d499a25b","tid":527282,"uid":137006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張櫈抽起你成個人果陣係驚到仆街，個心跳到痛<br />\n<br />\n但跌果下其實唔大離心力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得少少<br />\n<br />\n然後玩多次，但升上去果陣都係驚到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反而覺得升上去cool實曬好安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一升左上去我反而個心定曬<br />\n相反門口個過山車冇乜安全設施就真係嚇到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5ad91653e098a443006021e1b9c499147f5f40","tid":527282,"uid":24368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"今日玩完<br />\n寒冷感&gt;驚嚇感+離心力<br />\n一啲都唔驚"},{"pid":"f16778037f672ec3645bdcce90bdeba0ac80155c","tid":527282,"uid":77102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:33:42.000Z","msg":"玩之前唔好食咁飽<br />\n爬喺度玩好想嘔"},{"pid":"2d1f65b676839b7556af30faa16cedd9e07b7477","tid":527282,"uid":41009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T23:42:50.000Z","msg":"冇fastpass要等起碼4粒鐘"},{"pid":"1bdca4f108b2f99893625c2e3dd9553325846fc7","tid":527282,"uid":7245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T00:14:59.000Z","msg":"唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eba46456c44c71c234e229e5837b4e154636ad9","tid":527282,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T00:22:02.000Z","msg":"好玩 刺激"},{"pid":"694fbb6d12db3ae4226736c4a50b8f56a48ee4ec","tid":527282,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T00:48:07.000Z","msg":"排單人半個鐘"},{"pid":"9596658f5e24a8c317956f7a4efb7274dc0be00b","tid":527282,"uid":1430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T00:48:46.000Z","msg":"其實張凳抽起你果時最驚<br />\n係驚唔穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後沖落去果下離心力無想像咁大<br />\n係真係果下 其餘係咁尻fing<br />\n但視角一流 真心好似比隻龍夾住飛咁<br />\n<br />\n利申：平時勁驚離心力但都想玩多次"},{"pid":"ceb3f9a4d31ece6f961ab4c605ce0d40f01a05eb","tid":527282,"uid":108176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T02:04:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得第一下衝落去離心力好大<br />\n之後無咩野 倒後向下衝嗰兩下超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩完好想玩第二次 係我玩過最正既過山車<br />\n唔玩會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定要玩"},{"pid":"1870d8bbe83dd00495e1ca78ba6bd109f95fdc80","tid":527282,"uid":214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T02:09:45.000Z","msg":"唔玩就無野玩<br />\n其他個啲嘢戇尻到震<br />\n全部視覺效果除非你10-13歲先會enjoy到"},{"pid":"71f225ec05ec334c13d833fb5582965